{
  "stem": "19921.7",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I'm very proud of that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Jewish War Veterans have also a tape, which eventually I will show it to you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a short tape, half an hour tape.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Also a very, very broadly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's on display-- as a matter of fact, that tape is on display by the producer of that tape in Washington, DC, in-- in the museum, in the Holocaust Museum in Washington, DC.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a catalog is with it also, which also is on sale for the profit.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I definitely-- yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I speak to-- to children, high school levels.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I also addressed a symposium also with the-- with the high school teachers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was done at Ramsey College one year.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had 40 teachers assembled.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were four speakers altogether.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it went very, very well, true.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And yes, I do.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Whoever ask me through the Holocaust Center in Spring Valley.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And if somebody ask me privately, I do it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I do it just to inform people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Not one single penny is taken in, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I do that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was invited.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I'm very proud to say that I was invited by the class of 1995 just before the graduation at West Point.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I'm involved in West Point, so they know me there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They know partially my history, because I don't brag about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But they know it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I'm invite-- I'm involved in-- in the Jewish chapel there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I'm co-chairman of the Jewish activities at West Point.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "As you know, we have a beautiful chapel there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there's now about 60 Jewish cadets, girls and boys.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And so I'm invited to address the cadets in 1995 just before the graduation in April, '95, by the rabbi there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And it went very, very well too.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
